2005-04-04  Peter Saunders  <pajs@i-scream.org>

    Initial version. Only compiled on solaris - but seems to work.

    Makes use of efA flags, and also a 'o' flag for sorting..

    ps -o cpu ps -o mem

    will sort by that type.

