2004-03-06  Adam Sampson  <ats@offog.org>

    Make the network stats regexp simpler. Since /proc/net/dev is a fixed
    format, there's no need to use [[:space:]] and [[:digit:]]; a literal
    space and [0-9] will suffice.

    
